<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1323,1727,1873]" lastBlockId="7.[264,1323,284,430]" lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="8" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,482,1727,1753]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Color in life.</emphasis>
Head not banded, spotted or blotched, uniformly dark brown but slightly paler in gular region (
<figureCitation box="[630,704,1767,1793]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="6.[264,368,1652,1676]" captionTargetBox="[452,1126,283,1643]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[452,1126,742,1209]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 3. Head profiles of Gymnotus ardilai. (A) Holotype, (B) Paratypes." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/169560/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Fig. 
<number box="[688,704,1767,1793]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
). Numerous minute chromatophores speckled over branchiostegal membranes and ventral surface of head. Pectoral­fin rays dark brown or black, interradial membranes hyaline. Anal­fin never blotched, spotted or marked. Analfin rays and membrane dark gray or black on anterior 
<number box="[927,957,284,310]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" value="80.0">80</number>
% of its length, translucent on posterior 
<number box="[375,408,324,350]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" value="20.0">20</number>
%. Color variation is progressively correlated with size with larger individuals losing the light bands. Juvenals (
<quantity box="[645,729,364,390]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.4" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" unit="mm" value="34.0">34 mm</quantity>
TL) with 
<number box="[847,920,364,390]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" value="16.0" valueMax="17.0" valueMin="15.0">15–17</number>
thin well­defined pale bands (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="7.[264,368,748,772]" captionTargetBox="[264,1319,473,737]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[263,1320,472,741]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 4. Lateral view of immature G. ardilai, 34 mm TL." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/169561/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
Fig. 
<number box="[264,282,404,430]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" value="4.0">4</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption box="[264,915,748,772]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/169561/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" targetBox="[264,1319,473,737]" targetPageId="7">
