<paragraph blockId="8.[264,1323,283,870]" box="[312,629,724,750]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,503,724,750]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Common name</emphasis>
. Lamprea.
